---
title: Smart Beef and Mushroom Stew with Potatoes and Spinach
description: This hearty dinner has all the flavours of a traditional stew, but lightened up. Beef, potatoes, thyme, mushrooms and spinach are featured in this dish that's sure to warm you up from the inside out.
